text: Kate Ford (born 29 December 1976) is an English actress, known for portraying the role of Tracy Barlow on the long-running ITV soap opera Coronation Street from 2002 to 2007, and 2010 onwards. Ford was born and raised in Salford District, Greater Manchester, England. ==Other websites== * Category:1976 births Category:Living people Category:English television actors Category:Soap opera actors Category:Actors from Greater Manchester
